WEBVTT

00:07:29.167 --> 00:07:30.934
And what did he find?

00:07:30.958 --> 00:07:37.101
He found that people who are most likely
to vote for a populist party

00:07:37.125 --> 00:07:40.684
also were the ones most likely
to strongly disagree

00:07:40.708 --> 00:07:44.268
that vaccines were important,
safe or effective.

00:07:44.292 --> 00:07:45.934
What did we learn?

00:07:45.958 --> 00:07:51.059
Vaccines cannot escape
the political and social turbulence

00:07:51.083 --> 00:07:52.518
that surrounds it.

00:07:52.542 --> 00:07:57.934
Scientists were unprepared
for this tsunami of doubt

00:07:57.958 --> 00:08:00.684
and questions and distrust.